### Model fitting {.unnumbered}

Fit BA data.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
params_ba_init <- list(
  mu = 1,
  K = 1,
  beta = 1,
  beta_edges = 1
)

fit <- fit_hawkesNet(
      ev = sim$ev,
      params_init = params_ba_init,
      mark_type = "ba"
    )
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "Fitting took 47.14 seconds"
```


